lead_paragraph: Since winning the Masters, Danny Willett has taken his green jacket to Wimbledon, thrown out the first pitch at a New York Yankees game and enjoyed the celebrity that goes with being a major champion. Add in fatherhood and it's been a couple of fun months.

headline.print_headline: Masters Champ Danny Willett Eyes Greener Pastures at PGA
